The paper deals with using deep convolutional neural networks for detecting dynamic objects in grid maps, which is a problem commonly encountered in robotics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also involves computer vision techniques such as CNNs, which makes cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) another likely category. The use of deep learning methods also suggests cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as possible categories. Finally, since the paper deals with practical applications in robotics, cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also a possible category.
